&lt;p&gt;Ceph is an open-source, software-defined storage platform that combines block, file and object storage in one scalable infrastructure. In combination with Proxmox VE, Ceph forms a powerful and cost-efficient storage solution for virtualization environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By distributing storage directly across multiple nodes, no external SAN or NAS is needed. This makes Ceph ideal for modern hyperconverged infrastructures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="ceph-integrated-in-proxmox-ve"&gt;Ceph integrated in Proxmox VE&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proxmox VE includes native integration with Ceph, allowing storage to be managed directly from the Proxmox web interface.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Proxmox Support</title><link>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/proxmox/proxmox-support/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/proxmox/proxmox-support/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Proxmox VE</title><link>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/proxmox/proxmox-ve/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/proxmox/proxmox-ve/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Refurbished Hardware</title><link>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/hardware-software/hardware/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/hardware-software/hardware/</guid><description/></item><item><title>VCF 5.x to VCF 9, Migration &amp; Upgrade</title><link>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/migratie/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/migratie/</guid><description/></item><item><title>VCF Automation</title><link>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vcf-automation/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vcf-automation/</guid><description/></item><item><title>VCF Operations</title><link>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vcf-operations/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vcf-operations/</guid><description/></item><item><title>VMware NSX 9</title><link>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/nsx/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/nsx/</guid><description/></item><item><title>VMware vSAN 9</title><link>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vsan/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vsan/</guid><description/></item><item><title>VMware vSphere 9</title><link>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vsphere/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vsphere/</guid><description/></item><item><title>vSphere Kubernetes Service (VKS)</title><link>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vsphere-kubernetes-service/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mademy.nl/en/diensten/vmware-cloud-foundation/vsphere-kubernetes-service/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>